Extra little helpful tip that I learned the hard way: if you put pictures in your fics, try not to use Imgur as your hosting site, as it got banned in the UK a few years ago, making your pics unviewable to UK readers. 
I’ve personally been using https://images.squidge.org/, which has been working great.
